{"tid":1025211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解地盤佬要比d女仔咁睇唔起","createTime":"2019-02-17T07:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T10:09:16.000Z","uid":205734,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a96b15732f8c62e04f528c5d244207b9dd99985f","tid":1025211,"uid":205734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"雖然做得呢行都係讀唔成書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔見得紀律部隊個d讀得成書，但又受女仔歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地盤佬腳踏實地辛辛苦苦靠對手去搵食又唔係做犯法<br />\n但d女人一聽到地盤呢個字就開始嫌棄人地<br />\n憑咩人地要比你地睇唔起on99，到底呢個職業得罪左佢地d咩？<br />\n利申：唔係做地盤"},{"pid":"fac8e41ef4eeca71e310761ffa6c0e1925c8262c","tid":1025211,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"百貨撞百客"},{"pid":"2410ce2bce85077b30804a65e1563057faa395b2","tid":1025211,"uid":39608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"可為因為平時係街撞到既地盤佬俾人印象一般"},{"pid":"25bd5d98f3109a9529ab3acce8f681fdc1585981","tid":1025211,"uid":115584,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:56:43.000Z","msg":"係文化問題 大眾對地盤佬睇唔起 大部分女仔就自自然然認為其他人講嘅就係啱<br />\n正如社會叫你努力工作 搵到錢買樓 社會有一大批人都係過緊人地眼中成功嘅生活 <br />\n<br />\n又唔見外國做地盤會比人睇唔起，根本係只係大部分廢中廢老影響住一代人嘅諗法"},{"pid":"2704e38b0f030ec2e847cc72afa6febc65ec41be","tid":1025211,"uid":224645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"地盤仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2195a836ecdc9d5d3056fab27710ed678f12b22a","tid":1025211,"uid":229793,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"因為香港地盤佬出名食煙 飲酒 講粗口 叫雞<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個個都會</span></span>"},{"pid":"d38382784ba6d71c5ece125f6c5b1707b58cae9f","tid":1025211,"uid":29606,"like"